resources.string: You can provide colors and typography for your theme by building \'ProvidedColors\' and \`ProvidedTypography\`.
You can provide colors for your theme by building \'ProvidedColors\' and adding it to payload builder via \'setProvidedColors\'.
You can provide typography for your theme by building \'ProvidedTypography\' and adding it to payload builder via \'setProvidedTypography\'.
